# Internal development notes. Rule: any root-level .md file is
# gitignored UNLESS it's README.md. This protects against future
# "quick doc I wrote about the architecture" files accidentally
# ending up on GitHub. Same policy as the docs/ folder.
/*.md
!/README.md
